description:
Prepare for an adrenaline-fueled journey like no other with Colorful Boi! This captivating platformer boasts 63 levels of intense gameplay, filled with treacherous traps.
Colorful Boi will push your skills to the limit and deliver an unforgettable gaming experience.
Are you ready to conquer all the challenges and become the ultimate platforming champion? Jump into the vibrant world of Colorful Boi now!
name: Colorful Boi
